imple Lie algebras appear in the description of $F^p(E,a)$.\n  Applications to classification of KdV and Krichever-Novikov type equations\nwith respect to Backlund transformations are also briefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Dec 2012 20:53:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 May 2013 15:12:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-31"}
