esults represent a versatile method for the\ncharacterization of new quantum spin Hall materials systems, and confirm both\nthe existence and the robustness of the predicted edge channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Dec 2012 20:57:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2012 19:10:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
