\\bf (P1)}, and\nprove the $\\co\\np$-completeness of {\\bf (P2)}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2012 05:46:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Dec 2012 16:31:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2012 08:12:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-21"}
